title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Tennis Titlist Back for UA” [Headline in The Cincinnati Enquirer, 8 September 1982. Submitted by Joseph W. McNair, Cincinnati, who asks Who is to do the seeding? Is this what they mean by women's doubles?]
